IR:

* Iron Raptor watched as prowl transformed, but knew that it was useless. 
His wing was bronken and as disoriented as Prowl was, he should have at 
least known that.
She simply stands there and watches him transform back into robot mode, 
simply shaking her head and stepping a bit closer as he falls to his knees, 
lowering her head sne nudging him with her snout.
Prowl wasn't looking well and she knew that he would be a while to repair, 
but by the time they got to the Ark he should be fine.

But she stands still while Prowl gets up and climbs up on her back, shifting 
her body to get use to the new weight. It wasn't much and it wouldn't slow 
her down, not a problem.
Iron Raptor then beginst to move out of the forst and towards the plain 
again, taking the long way to the Ark.
She would walk a bit while Prowl repaired a bit, making sure not to jar him 
into pain or anything.*

" Now, Get repaired."

Desmonus:

* Desmonus coughed a bit as she sat up, the strike against the wall not 
really being what she would call the perfect ride.
She flapped her wings a few times to settle them before she got to her feet, 
steadying herself against the wall as the base stablized.
Brushing herself off she hardly noticed as BloodyStrike got to his feet and 
looked her over, stretching a bit to work out the kinks in her stressed 
gears.
This day was getting worse every moment.
First starvation and now a head on colision with a pair of bots.
Perfect.
Desmonus looks up  in a bit of surprise as she hears BloodyStrike speak, 
looking him over a bit and straightening her stance.
Her amber optics narrowed before her senses cought the small of his mech 
fluid.
She remembered that scent...but from where.
Desmonus relaxed a bit as she stood against the wall.*

" I'm fine...you?"
